{"tid":2281003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓬佩奧宣布美台下周舉行經濟對話　台灣經濟部次長率團　料談安全供應鍊及 5G","createTime":"2020-11-11T02:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T06:35:00.000Z","uid":53379,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"88d7f9c449128296869bcc9b998205645cbb97ae","tid":2281003,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T02:25:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">蓬佩奧宣布美台下周舉行經濟對話　台灣經濟部次長率團　料談安全供應鍊及 5G</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧宣布，曾在 9 月訪問台灣的次國務卿克拉赫（Keith Krach）下周五（20日）會主持與台灣的經濟對話，內容將觸及安全供應鍊和 5G 安保。蓬佩奧表示，對話是顯示美台的經濟關係，有助雙方增強各方面的合作，包括健康安全、安全供應鏈及 5G 潔淨網絡等。他又形容台灣是充滿活力的民主政體及可靠夥伴，正強大和持續茁壯。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%B0%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E9%83%A8%E6%AC%A1%E9%95%B7%E7%8E%87%E5%9C%98-%E6%96%99%E8%AB%87%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E9%8D%8A%E5%8F%8A-5g/?fbclid=IwAR084ewg6tKnaOrbYiSM8w6KccAaploqbi4KG52Waa5l7W9bRTKtqMzqa6s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%258F%25B0%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%258E%2587%25E5%259C%2598-%25E6%2596%2599%25E8%25AB%2587%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E9%258D%258A%25E5%258F%258A-5g%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR084ewg6tKnaOrbYiSM8w6KccAaploqbi4KG52Waa5l7W9bRTKtqMzqa6s&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=b2475f2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E7%25